author: Matt Walsh
description:
Today on The Matt Walsh Show, I was attacked by both sides of the aisle over the weekend. What did I say this time that caused such outrage? We will discuss. Also, Portland leftists found a new and unique way to protest outside of an ICE facility. MTG goes on CNN to apologize for her rhetoric. What is she doing? And, Vice releases a new, feminist, whiny article about "mankeeping". There is a bigger point that needs to be discussed about this "mankeeping" and we will get into it today.
